      <p><strong>18.5</strong> If a deal lapses due to negligence on the part of the closer, such as insufficient follow-up, incorrect information or non-compliance with agreed processes, ClosersMatch may withhold outstanding commissions or offset them against the damage suffered by the client.</p>
