      <h2 id="article-19">Article 19 – Invoicing, payment and platform fee</h2>
      <p><strong>19.1</strong> ClosersMatch acts solely as an intermediary between client and closer. ClosersMatch is not an employer, main contractor or principal, and does not handle payroll or VAT administration on behalf of closers.</p>
