      <p><strong>19.4</strong> After confirmation of a successful deal, the closer must issue an invoice addressed to the client, containing:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>a) the closer's full company details and VAT number;</li>
        <li>b) the client's name with the notation "via ClosersMatch";</li>
